name: 69 Boyz
description: '''69 Boyz''' is an American [[Miami bass]] and [[hip hop music|hip hop]] duo: Van "Thrill Da Playa" Bryant, from [[Jacksonville, Florida|Jacksonville]], [[Florida]], and Barry "Fast" Wright, from [[Orlando, Florida]], United States. The group was initiated by Thrill Da Playa with the assistance of producers C.C. Lemonhead and Jay Ski (of Chill Deal, [[Quad City DJs]], and [[95 South]]).
